Your attitude, not your aptitude, will determine your altitude.

When life gets hard and you want to give up, remember that life is full of ups and downs, and without the downs, the ups would mean nothing.
There is only one thing that makes a dream impossible to achieve: the fear of failure.
When one door of happiness closes, another opens; but often we look so long at the closed door that we do not see the one which has been opened for us.
Sometimes the hardest part isn't letting go, but rather, learning to start over.
Opportunities are not offered. They must be wrested and worked for. And this calls for perseverance and courage.

Remember, happiness doesn't depend upon who you are or what you have; it depends solely upon what you think.
Sometimes things have to fall apart to make way for better things.
It's not about making the amazing saves. It's the little things and small things that made great gatekeepers great.
The turning point in the process of growing up is when you discover the core of strength within you that survives all hurt.

data.Content:
◼︎职位要求:
①.大专以上学历，计算机软件或理工科专业毕业；文科类毕业生要求有两年以上软件开发经验。
◆中国国内招聘的経験少日本語弱的技術者，可在蘇州带薪培训半年左右后再来日本工作。
②.掌握MCFrame、JAVA、SAP 、ERP、EBS、 dynamics、oracle cloud、BI publisher、Ruby、Python、.NET(ASP・VB・C#)、C/C++、iOS、android、PHP、PL/SQL 等其中任意一种开发语言。
◼︎日语要求：
日语能力2级以上，能够阅读理解日文式样书，能够用日语简单交流。
◼︎工作地点：
日本东京都及周边地区，大阪，京都，名古屋，广岛，富山，福冈等地区。
◼︎薪资水平：
20万～100万日元/月収。
（完全视日语水平和技术水平而定）
■福利制度：
带薪休假+健康保险+厚生年金+加班费+交通费+雇佣保险+社员旅行等。
■联系方式：
Infor@jp.highwayns.com
■欢迎朋友帮助扩散
